Class UpdateBatch

  • entity.UpdateBatch
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Bean, Versionable

    public class UpdateBatch
implements Bean, Versionable
    UpdateBatch has been deprecated since ClaimCenter 8.0 along with the IAddressBookAdapter.
